| Feature           | CBOW                    | Skip-Gram                                |
| ----------------- | ----------------------- | ---------------------------------------- |
| Full Form         | Continuous Bag of Words | Skip-Gram                                |
| Input             | Context Words           | Target Word                              |
| Output            | Target Word             | Context Words                            |
| Number of Inputs  | Multiple                | One                                      |
| Number of Outputs | One                     | Multiple                                 |
| Training Speed    | Faster                  | Slower                                   |
| Best For          | Frequent words          | Rare words                               |
| Accuracy          | Good                    | Better for small datasets and rare words |


